organization.description:
As the sole member of the Feeding America network serving South Florida, Feeding South Florida is one of 200 food banks throughout the United States. Feeding South Florida has the largest service area in the state of Florida, serving 25% of the stateGu00c7u00d6s food insecure population throughout Palm Beach, Broward, Miami-Dade, and Monroe Counties. Food is distributed to direct service programs and a network of approximately 360 nonprofit partner agencies.
